{"tid":1443440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【認識心理學＋學術】阻路冇用？你班廢物同我入來溫書","createTime":"2019-08-11T08:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:53.000Z","uid":66087,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bcbcc71c39bcc2c57eac0d6b481f6f8bc7cc6c0","tid":1443440,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:26:41.000Z","msg":"近排連登好明顯出現好多分化聲音，<strong>好明顯係有對家勢力滲入。</strong><br />\n<br />\n對家經常提到一點，就係塞地鐵，噴交通燈... 唔work，叫大家停哂手腳。<br />\n<br />\n事實係，<strong>「不合作運動」初期會有阻力，但最終會嚴重損害政府民望。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一幅圖解釋：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/V4Lb8tE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4Lb8tE.png&h=1ef95919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國心理學家Julian Bernard Rotter 控制點理論講過，人會對情境既解釋會轉變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用人話講&mdash;&mdash;<strong>堵塞地鐵初期，社會有聲音怪罪示威者，但隨著時間推移，反對聲音會減少，民眾會搵出真正原因&mdash;&mdash;政府管治不當導致市民抗拒政權，最後，大眾必定怪罪政府。</strong><br />\n<br />\nAll in all，<strong>不合作係一場持久戰，只要繼續做，我地一定會係勝利方！</strong>"},{"pid":"ff929004bb5e20f708173a7bcbc1c48ffab91740","tid":1443440,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd257f3fdec7536d59a76a41f3e560cac150a640","tid":1443440,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"因為政府鋪天蓋地「止暴制亂」口號，仲未未shift到人怪政府，點搞"}]}